21
00:01:36,790 --> 00:01:39,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">[Episode 40]</font>

22
00:01:39,920 --> 00:01:40,480
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Apprehend her.</font>

23
00:01:40,760 --> 00:01:41,200
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Yes.</font>

24
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:44,920
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Kill him!</font>

25
00:01:53,070 --> 00:01:53,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Protect the Emperor!</font>

26
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:54,710
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Protect the Emperor!</font>

27
00:02:01,230 --> 00:02:02,000
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Your Majesty.</font>

28
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:57,120
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I left the Shen Pavilion
without permission.</font>

29
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:58,360
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Please punish me, Your Majesty.</font>

30
00:02:59,150 --> 00:02:59,960
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Yanxi.</font>

31
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:01,710
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You should get a reward.</font>

32
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:03,150
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">The Security Bureau</font>

33
00:03:03,310 --> 00:03:04,750
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">found out and removed the fire caltrops.</font>

34
00:03:04,870 --> 00:03:06,280
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">It's another credit of yours.</font>

35
00:03:06,750 --> 00:03:07,840
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I dare not claim the credit.</font>

36
00:03:08,590 --> 00:03:09,800
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">It wasn't the Security Bureau Guards</font>

37
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:11,190
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">that spotted the fire caltrops.</font>

38
00:03:11,310 --> 00:03:11,910
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Then who spotted that?</font>

39
00:03:16,710 --> 00:03:17,400
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">It was you.</font>

40
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:20,520
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Come here.</font>

41
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:28,280
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Tell me.</font>

42
00:03:28,590 --> 00:03:29,710
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">How did you know?</font>

43
00:03:30,590 --> 00:03:32,030
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">The sulfur smell of those fireworks
was too strong.</font>

44
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:33,240
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Once they explode,</font>

45
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:34,470
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">countless people will get hurt.</font>

46
00:03:55,030 --> 00:03:56,120
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I wanted my fire caltrops to kill</font>

47
00:03:56,190 --> 00:03:57,150
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">those who had it coming.</font>

48
00:03:58,960 --> 00:04:00,840
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You are a spy of the Zhao Empire, right?</font>

49
00:04:01,710 --> 00:04:03,080
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">But you are good.</font>

50
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:04,960
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You turned my trusted officials
against me</font>

51
00:04:05,430 --> 00:04:06,960
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">and deceived my people.</font>

52
00:04:07,470 --> 00:04:08,520
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Even the Security Bureau</font>

53
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:09,800
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">couldn't find anything on you.</font>

54
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,750
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">If you had behaved yourself</font>

55
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:13,680
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">and served as the Dubhe Envoy,</font>

56
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,840
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I might have let you live
a few more days.</font>

57
00:04:16,430 --> 00:04:18,160
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You are too impatient.</font>

58
00:04:20,750 --> 00:04:21,310
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You are right.</font>

59
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:23,800
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I am from the Zhao Empire.</font>

60
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:34,630
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">What a coincidence.</font>

61
00:04:35,630 --> 00:04:36,750
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You are not the only one who remembers</font>

62
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:39,040
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">everything about the battle
at Kushui River.</font>

63
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:41,240
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I too can never forget it.</font>

64
00:04:43,830 --> 00:04:44,630
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">My father.</font>

65
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:46,120
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">My elder brother.</font>

66
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:47,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">My uncle.</font>

67
00:04:48,310 --> 00:04:49,040
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">They were all killed</font>

68
00:04:49,070 --> 00:04:50,270
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">by your soldiers.</font>

69
00:04:51,390 --> 00:04:52,480
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">My mother and I went to the battlefield</font>

70
00:04:52,630 --> 00:04:53,560
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">to search for their bodies</font>

71
00:04:54,310 --> 00:04:55,800
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">for three days and three nights.</font>

72
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:56,750
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Our fingers were even bleeding,</font>

73
00:04:56,870 --> 00:04:58,310
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">but we never found
the remains of my family.</font>

74
00:04:59,360 --> 00:04:59,920
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">After a while,</font>

75
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:02,120
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">my mother starved to death.</font>

76
00:05:03,270 --> 00:05:05,120
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I followed the refugees to the Capital</font>

77
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:07,830
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">and served under Emperor Huai.</font>

78
00:05:08,390 --> 00:05:10,000
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I was raised as a spy.</font>

79
00:05:10,630 --> 00:05:12,310
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">As long as I can avenge my family,</font>

80
00:05:13,070 --> 00:05:14,190
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I'm willing to do anything.</font>

81
00:05:19,630 --> 00:05:21,000
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">She is actually a spy
of the Zhao Empire.</font>

82
00:05:22,190 --> 00:05:23,800
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">The spies who trained with me</font>

83
00:05:23,950 --> 00:05:25,830
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">entered your country one after another.</font>

84
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:27,270
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">And they were killed</font>

85
00:05:27,310 --> 00:05:28,040
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">without anyone noticing.</font>

86
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:29,270
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Many of them</font>

87
00:05:29,270 --> 00:05:30,430
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">were hunted down by the Security Bureau.</font>

88
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:31,950
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">And me?</font>

89
00:05:34,160 --> 00:05:35,070
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I am different.</font>

90
00:05:35,950 --> 00:05:37,270
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I am the best of those spies.</font>

91
00:05:37,720 --> 00:05:38,560
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I made it into the Imperial Capital</font>

92
00:05:38,630 --> 00:05:39,600
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">and I even entered the Palace.</font>

93
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:40,950
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I was just a step away</font>

94
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:41,950
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">to have you killed.</font>

95
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:43,870
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">At that battle,</font>

96
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:47,070
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">you were not the only one
who was grieving.</font>

97
00:05:48,750 --> 00:05:50,000
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">The families of those soldiers
and civilians</font>

98
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:50,950
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">who died in that war also grieved.</font>

99
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:53,240
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">And you,</font>

100
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:54,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">to satisfy</font>

101
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:55,750
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Emperor Huai's endless ambition,</font>

102
00:05:56,270 --> 00:05:57,480
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">have started wars with us
again and again.</font>

103
00:05:58,270 --> 00:05:58,950
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Have you ever considered</font>

104
00:05:59,040 --> 00:06:00,120
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">the well-being of the people
from both realms?</font>

105
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:01,160
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">What about my family?</font>

106
00:06:02,390 --> 00:06:02,920
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Do you mean</font>

107
00:06:02,950 --> 00:06:04,190
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">their deaths don't matter?</font>

108
00:06:04,950 --> 00:06:06,310
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I don't care what Emperor Huai wants.</font>

109
00:06:07,390 --> 00:06:08,600
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I just want to avenge my family.</font>

110
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:10,720
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Blood will have blood.</font>

111
00:06:11,390 --> 00:06:12,600
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You are way out of your league</font>

112
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:14,120
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">and don't know what you are doing.</font>

113
00:06:14,800 --> 00:06:15,360
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Is that so?</font>

114
00:06:16,240 --> 00:06:18,600
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">If Gu Yanxi hadn't been here in time,</font>

115
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:20,800
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">you would be a cold corpse by now.</font>

116
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:23,120
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You must be scared, right?</font>

117
00:06:24,310 --> 00:06:25,270
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Back when I trained as a spy,</font>

118
00:06:25,270 --> 00:06:26,120
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I often wondered</font>

119
00:06:27,270 --> 00:06:28,680
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">what the mighty Emperor of Daqing</font>

120
00:06:28,920 --> 00:06:30,360
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">was like.</font>

121
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:32,040
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">How truly fearsome</font>

122
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:33,040
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">and formidable could he be?</font>

123
00:06:34,190 --> 00:06:35,240
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Until I met you.</font>

124
00:06:35,950 --> 00:06:36,680
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Only then did I realize</font>

125
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:38,870
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">you were nothing</font>

126
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:40,190
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">but a weak and paranoid old man!</font>

127
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:41,720
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You not only are aged,</font>

128
00:06:42,510 --> 00:06:43,950
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">but you are also a coward.</font>

129
00:06:44,920 --> 00:06:46,560
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You are afraid
of your courtiers' criticism.</font>

130
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:48,190
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You are afraid
of your own siblings and offspring.</font>

131
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:49,920
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You are afraid of your own people.</font>

132
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:50,630
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You are so afraid</font>

133
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:51,560
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">that you drive everyone away.</font>

134
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:53,120
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Even Gu Yanxi
has turned his back on you.</font>

135
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:55,360
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You know too well that I am a charlatan,</font>

136
00:06:55,510 --> 00:06:56,560
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">but you still want to use me.</font>

137
00:06:57,430 --> 00:06:58,720
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">There's one thing you don't know.</font>

138
00:06:59,950 --> 00:07:01,480
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Even your own son...</font>

139
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:33,430
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Just a lowly wench!</font>

140
00:07:33,950 --> 00:07:35,070
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">How dare she talk so much nonsense</font>

141
00:07:35,070 --> 00:07:36,000
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">in front of the Emperor?</font>

142
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:38,270
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You are just useless.</font>

143
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:40,120
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You just stand and watch her
causing a stir here?</font>

144
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:41,270
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Dump her somewhere.</font>

145
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:41,720
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Yes.</font>

146
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:43,920
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">This is good.</font>

147
00:07:44,510 --> 00:07:46,560
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">That's how a royal heir
should carry himself.</font>

148
00:07:48,190 --> 00:07:48,800
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">However,</font>

149
00:07:49,160 --> 00:07:50,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">the spy doesn't matter.</font>

150
00:07:50,950 --> 00:07:52,390
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Now I really wonder</font>

151
00:07:52,750 --> 00:07:54,430
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">why you saved me.</font>

152
00:07:57,720 --> 00:07:58,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Your Majesty, you misunderstand me.</font>

153
00:07:58,800 --> 00:08:00,000
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">It wasn't just about you.</font>

154
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:01,480
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">If there had been an explosion,</font>

155
00:08:01,630 --> 00:08:03,240
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">you wouldn't be the only one dead.</font>

156
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:04,920
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">During the chaos,</font>

157
00:08:05,190 --> 00:08:06,160
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">many people would die</font>

158
00:08:06,390 --> 00:08:07,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">in Daqing and the Zhao Empire.</font>

159
00:08:09,240 --> 00:08:09,720
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Guards!</font>

160
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:12,360
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I don't want to see her again.</font>

161
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:13,040
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">As you command.</font>

162
00:08:18,950 --> 00:08:20,480
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">She saved your life, Your Majesty.</font>

163
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:34,550
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I have divined for you, Your Highness.</font>

164
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:35,720
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You</font>

165
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:37,320
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">are destined to be a true dragon.</font>

166
00:08:37,750 --> 00:08:38,840
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">The supreme throne</font>

167
00:08:39,550 --> 00:08:40,720
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">will soon be yours.</font>

168
00:08:41,510 --> 00:08:42,080
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">And I am willing</font>

169
00:08:42,550 --> 00:08:43,630
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">to be your follower.</font>

170
00:08:45,150 --> 00:08:46,390
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">This poison is called green stone.</font>

171
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:48,120
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">He will be killed within fifteen minutes</font>

172
00:08:48,910 --> 00:08:49,960
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">after he takes it.</font>

173
00:08:50,720 --> 00:08:52,000
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">It will be the Longevity Festival
in a few days.</font>

174
00:08:52,910 --> 00:08:53,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Your Highness.</font>

175
00:08:53,870 --> 00:08:55,200
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You must seize the opportunity.</font>

176
00:08:57,750 --> 00:08:58,320
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Your Majesty.</font>

