189
00:09:53,270 --> 00:09:54,840
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">His Majesty only had one drink tonight.</font>

190
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:56,790
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">And that was from Lord Hui.</font>

191
00:09:58,870 --> 00:09:59,960
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Since when a mere eunuch</font>

192
