<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">His Majesty is still alive.</font>

194
00:10:05,870 --> 00:10:07,120
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">How dare you all defect?</font>

195
00:10:07,510 --> 00:10:08,150
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">If he really is</font>

196
00:10:08,150 --> 00:10:09,390
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">a regicidal and patricidal usurper,</font>

197
00:10:10,390 --> 00:10:11,670
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">would you still serve him
as the new Emperor?</font>

198
00:10:15,270 --> 00:10:15,750
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Shut up.</font>

199
00:10:16,030 --> 00:10:16,910
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Shut up!</font>

200
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:18,390
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Listen to me.</font>

201
00:10:18,910 --> 00:10:19,840
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Those who assist me today</font>

202
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:21,320
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">will be credited greatly.</font>

203
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:22,120
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You will enjoy</font>

204
00:10:22,480 --> 00:10:24,320
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">endless glory and wealth
once I become the Emperor.</font>

205
00:10:32,150 --> 00:10:33,150
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">This is the antidote.</font>

206
00:10:33,390 --> 00:10:34,080
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Please keep it, Your Highness.</font>

207
00:10:34,670 --> 00:10:36,030
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">When the time comes,
place it in your mouth</font>

208
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:37,750
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">and it will neutralize the poison
of the green stone.</font>

209
00:10:38,910 --> 00:10:39,630
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">This evil witch.</font>

210
00:10:40,480 --> 00:10:41,270
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Seize him!</font>

211
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:44,910
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Nobody moves.</font>

212
00:10:46,390 --> 00:10:47,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Or I'll kill him.</font>

213
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:48,550
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Stand back.</font>

214
