<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Uncle.</font>

217
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:06,360
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Imperial physician.</font>

218
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:07,840
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Bring the imperial physician!</font>

219
