<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Uncle.</font>

220
00:11:19,150 --> 00:11:19,720
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Uncle.</font>

221
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:22,240
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I will definitely hunt down</font>

222
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:24,000
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">the remnants
of Lord Hui and Haoyue's faction.</font>

223
00:11:24,790 --> 00:11:25,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I'll keep the peace.</font>

224
00:11:31,120 --> 00:11:31,750
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Uncle.</font>

225
00:11:40,120 --> 00:11:40,790
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I realize it now.</font>

226
00:11:43,720 --> 00:11:45,030
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I don't hate you at all.</font>

227
00:11:47,840 --> 00:11:48,670
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Growing up,</font>

228
00:11:50,030 --> 00:11:51,550
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I have always regarded you as my father.</font>

229
00:11:54,750 --> 00:11:55,750
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">When I was in the northern land,</font>

230
00:11:57,720 --> 00:11:58,840
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I would often think of you.</font>

231
00:12:01,510 --> 00:12:02,240
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Because I knew</font>

232
00:12:04,120 --> 00:12:04,840
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">that one day</font>

233
00:12:06,630 --> 00:12:07,480
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">you would summon me back</font>

234
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:09,910
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">to your side.</font>

235
00:12:15,870 --> 00:12:17,080
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I know that it was you</font>

236
00:12:17,150 --> 00:12:17,910
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">who asked Qi Ruhai to frame me.</font>

237
00:12:20,510 --> 00:12:21,720
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I also know that you need me.</font>

238
00:12:22,750 --> 00:12:23,720
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Daqing needs me.</font>

239
00:12:25,270 --> 00:12:26,240
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">So I came back.</font>

240
00:12:28,480 --> 00:12:29,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">This is my destiny.</font>

241
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:34,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Don't worry.</font>

242
00:12:36,910 --> 00:12:38,360
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">As long as I am the Commander
of the Security Bureau,</font>

243
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:41,240
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I will always be a sword</font>

244
00:12:41,870 --> 00:12:43,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">that guards you and Daqing.</font>

245
00:12:45,720 --> 00:12:47,670
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Yanxi...</font>

246
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:40,440
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">The...</font>

247
00:13:41,200 --> 00:13:42,550
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">The royal heir is...</font>

248
00:13:43,150 --> 00:13:44,670
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">What should we do now?</font>

249
00:13:45,080 --> 00:13:46,240
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">People will know soon.</font>

250
00:13:46,510 --> 00:13:47,120
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">When the day comes,</font>

251
00:13:47,360 --> 00:13:48,150
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">it will cause great chaos</font>

252
00:13:48,360 --> 00:13:49,270
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">across the land.</font>

253
00:13:51,270 --> 00:13:53,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Empress Dowager is here.</font>

254
00:14:08,360 --> 00:14:10,120
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You don't need to worry.</font>

255
00:14:11,870 --> 00:14:13,320
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">The Gu Family still</font>

256
00:14:13,790 --> 00:14:14,910
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">has a royal heir left.</font>

257
00:14:59,670 --> 00:15:00,360
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">We</font>

258
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:03,120
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">are grateful for the Emperor's grace.</font>

259
00:15:05,750 --> 00:15:06,720
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Congratulations.</font>

260
00:15:07,150 --> 00:15:08,200
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Please pack up your things</font>

261
00:15:08,320 --> 00:15:09,600
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">and depart for the Capital.</font>

262
00:15:17,870 --> 00:15:18,790
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Great news!</font>

263
00:15:19,150 --> 00:15:20,120
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">They are so lucky.</font>

264
00:15:20,550 --> 00:15:20,910
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Up.</font>

265
00:15:23,360 --> 00:15:23,840
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Pingyu.</font>

266
00:15:25,910 --> 00:15:27,360
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Is it because we have a new Emperor?</font>

267
00:15:28,030 --> 00:15:28,840
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Don't talk nonsense.</font>

268
00:15:29,510 --> 00:15:30,000
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Pingyu.</font>

269
00:15:30,600 --> 00:15:32,670
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Can we really
return to the Imperial Capital?</font>

270
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:33,840
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I never thought</font>

271
00:15:33,840 --> 00:15:34,480
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">we could be released so soon.</font>

272
00:15:34,960 --> 00:15:35,960
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I bet</font>

273
00:15:36,270 --> 00:15:37,390
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">it was all thanks to Zhi.</font>

274
00:15:37,510 --> 00:15:38,670
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">She said she would bring us home.</font>

275
00:15:38,790 --> 00:15:39,270
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I just knew</font>

276
00:15:39,390 --> 00:15:40,200
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">she could make it happen.</font>

277
00:15:42,120 --> 00:15:42,630
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Boyu.</font>

278
00:15:43,510 --> 00:15:44,630
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Your mother must have prepared</font>

279
00:15:44,670 --> 00:15:45,750
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">lots of good food and drinks</font>

280
00:15:45,750 --> 00:15:46,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">for the two of us.</font>

281
00:15:46,720 --> 00:15:47,240
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I think</font>

282
00:15:47,270 --> 00:15:48,480
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Jin'e wants Boyu back.</font>

283
00:15:48,630 --> 00:15:49,550
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">But you? I am not sure.</font>

284
00:15:49,630 --> 00:15:50,030
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Let's go.</font>

285
00:15:50,550 --> 00:15:51,150
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Time to go home.</font>

286
00:15:51,600 --> 00:15:52,270
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">We need to tell Father</font>

287
00:15:52,840 --> 00:15:53,270
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">about this.</font>

288
00:15:53,360 --> 00:15:53,750
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Let's go.</font>

289
00:15:54,150 --> 00:15:54,600
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Wait.</font>

290
00:15:58,720 --> 00:16:00,030
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">The Emperor has already pardoned us.</font>

291
00:16:00,790 --> 00:16:01,390
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Now</font>

292
00:16:01,910 --> 00:16:02,630
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">we are no longer prisoners.</font>

293
00:16:02,910 --> 00:16:03,550
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Mr. Hua.</font>

294
00:16:04,270 --> 00:16:05,000
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I am</font>

295
00:16:05,360 --> 00:16:06,120
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">a blundering boor.</font>

296
00:16:06,360 --> 00:16:07,240
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I have offended you a lot in the past,</font>

297
00:16:07,480 --> 00:16:08,320
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">but I know you are magnanimous,</font>

298
00:16:08,480 --> 00:16:09,390
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">so please forgive me.</font>

299
00:16:09,510 --> 00:16:10,080
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Officer.</font>

300
00:16:10,720 --> 00:16:11,720
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Just say it if you want anything.</font>

301
00:16:12,360 --> 00:16:13,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Could you do me a favor</font>

302
00:16:13,550 --> 00:16:14,720
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">when you go back?</font>

303
00:16:14,960 --> 00:16:15,840
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Please take my letter to my family.</font>

304
00:16:16,080 --> 00:16:16,600
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">It's been several years</font>

305
00:16:16,600 --> 00:16:17,670
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">since I have last seen them.</font>

306
00:16:18,030 --> 00:16:18,670
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I don't even know</font>

307
00:16:18,750 --> 00:16:20,120
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">what my child looks like now.</font>

308
00:16:20,480 --> 00:16:20,910
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Alright.</font>

309
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:22,360
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">How about this?</font>

310
00:16:22,630 --> 00:16:24,030
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Write down what you want to say,</font>

311
00:16:24,200 --> 00:16:25,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">then have Boyu
transcribe it into a letter.</font>

312
00:16:25,750 --> 00:16:26,550
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">And we will surely deliver it for you.</font>

313
00:16:27,000 --> 00:16:27,360
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">No problem.</font>

314
00:16:27,480 --> 00:16:28,270
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I'll write it down right now.</font>

315
00:16:29,240 --> 00:16:29,670
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Please help me too.</font>

316
00:16:29,960 --> 00:16:30,910
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I want that too.</font>

317
00:16:31,150 --> 00:16:32,200
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Please help me.</font>

318
00:16:32,320 --> 00:16:33,200
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Please also deliver a letter for me.</font>

319
00:16:33,550 --> 00:16:34,360
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Count me in.</font>

320
00:16:39,360 --> 00:16:39,910
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Everyone.</font>

321
00:16:40,120 --> 00:16:41,550
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Each of you write down</font>

322
00:16:41,630 --> 00:16:42,390
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">what you want to say.</font>

323
00:16:42,600 --> 00:16:43,840
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">We will take it to your family, okay?</font>

324
00:16:44,080 --> 00:16:45,240
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">- Okay.
- Thank you.</font>

325
00:16:54,550 --> 00:16:55,360
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Your Majesty, you are distracted.</font>

326
00:16:55,870 --> 00:16:56,630
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Yanxi.</font>

327
00:16:57,270 --> 00:16:58,270
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">A few days ago,</font>

328
00:16:58,390 --> 00:16:59,960
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I have absolved the men
of the Hua Family</font>

329
00:17:00,360 --> 00:17:01,270
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">and they are permitted to return.</font>

330
00:17:01,910 --> 00:17:02,840
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">It's been so many days.</font>

331
00:17:03,200 --> 00:17:04,000
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">They should have arrived by now.</font>

332
00:17:07,440 --> 00:17:08,070
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Mr. Shen.</font>

333
00:17:08,960 --> 00:17:09,440
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Your Majesty.</font>

334
00:17:10,350 --> 00:17:11,400
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You've come just in time.</font>

335
00:17:11,680 --> 00:17:12,590
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Playing Go gives me a headache.</font>

336
00:17:13,000 --> 00:17:13,790
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You can play with His Majesty.</font>

337
00:17:14,070 --> 00:17:14,590
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I still have things to do.</font>

338
00:17:14,790 --> 00:17:15,270
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I'll leave now.</font>

339
00:17:16,350 --> 00:17:17,550
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">What makes you so hurried?</font>

340
00:17:17,790 --> 00:17:18,350
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Don't you know?</font>

341
00:17:19,110 --> 00:17:20,350
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">The men of the Hua Family
will return today.</font>

342
00:17:20,590 --> 00:17:21,750
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I'm going to greet them with Hua Zhi.</font>

343
00:17:22,440 --> 00:17:24,030
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Why didn't Hua Zhi tell me about it?</font>

344
00:17:24,270 --> 00:17:25,440
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You're not part of the Hua Family.</font>

345
00:17:25,830 --> 00:17:26,550
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Why should she tell you?</font>

346
00:17:27,200 --> 00:17:27,680
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">See you later.</font>

347
00:17:38,240 --> 00:17:39,270
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">We will see them soon.</font>

348
00:17:39,350 --> 00:17:40,110
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">How come they haven't arrived yet?</font>

349
00:17:40,830 --> 00:17:41,440
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">That's wonderful.</font>

350
00:17:41,640 --> 00:17:42,160
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">They will be here soon.</font>

351
00:17:45,590 --> 00:17:46,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Why haven't they come yet?</font>

352
00:17:46,920 --> 00:17:47,440
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Wait a little longer.</font>

353
00:17:48,160 --> 00:17:48,960
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">How do I look?</font>

354
00:17:49,750 --> 00:17:50,720
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Very beautiful.</font>

355
00:17:51,550 --> 00:17:52,440
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I don't want to look good.</font>

356
00:17:52,510 --> 00:17:53,480
