His Majesty was enraged.</font>

422
00:21:48,350 --> 00:21:49,400
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">And thus we went through this calamity.</font>

423
00:21:50,510 --> 00:21:52,830
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I had no regrets at first.</font>

424
00:21:54,590 --> 00:21:56,200
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I was just exiled to the northern land.</font>

425
00:21:56,960 --> 00:21:58,240
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">It was nothing.</font>

426
00:21:59,920 --> 00:22:00,640
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">However,</font>

427
00:22:01,720 --> 00:22:02,350
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Wan,</font>

428
00:22:03,960 --> 00:22:05,480
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">you're the one</font>

429
00:22:06,830 --> 00:22:07,830
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I'm most sorry for.</font>

430
00:22:09,200 --> 00:22:10,720
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I didn't know the last time we met</font>

431
00:22:12,160 --> 00:22:13,790
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">would be the last time of our lives.</font>

432
00:22:15,720 --> 00:22:16,590
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Fortunately,</font>

433
00:22:17,880 --> 00:22:19,200
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">it won't take me</font>

434
00:22:20,310 --> 00:22:21,750
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">too long</font>

435
00:22:22,510 --> 00:22:24,110
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">to reunite with you.</font>

436
00:22:25,400 --> 00:22:27,030
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">When I come to find you in heaven,</font>

437
00:22:27,680 --> 00:22:29,000
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">you can blame me as you want.</font>

438
00:22:29,760 --> 00:22:32,350
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">[Memorial Tablet of Madam Hua]</font>

439
00:22:36,030 --> 00:22:37,750
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Both of you came here with me.</font>

440
00:22:38,640 --> 00:22:39,640
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Do you have something</font>

441
00:22:40,110 --> 00:22:41,030
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">that you want to say to her?</font>

442
00:22:55,310 --> 00:22:55,790
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Madam Hua.</font>

443
00:22:56,790 --> 00:22:57,440
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">We brought you</font>

444
00:22:57,480 --> 00:22:58,350
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">new pastries from the Hua's.</font>

445
00:22:59,440 --> 00:23:00,000
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Please have a taste.</font>

446
00:23:00,390 --> 00:23:02,460
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">[Memorial Tablet of Madam Hua]</font>

447
00:23:02,590 --> 00:23:03,960
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You are a smart child.</font>

448
00:23:04,510 --> 00:23:05,790
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Be true to yourself.</font>

449
00:23:06,310 --> 00:23:08,000
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Do you like that master of martial arts?</font>

450
00:23:08,440 --> 00:23:09,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">If one day,</font>

451
00:23:09,680 --> 00:23:10,790
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">you have your answer,</font>

452
00:23:11,070 --> 00:23:11,960
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">no matter who that is,</font>

453
00:23:12,200 --> 00:23:13,750
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">just come tell me.</font>

454
00:23:14,590 --> 00:23:15,160
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Grandmother.</font>

455
00:23:16,350 --> 00:23:17,480
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You asked me</font>

456
00:23:18,350 --> 00:23:19,030
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">if I already knew</font>

457
00:23:19,110 --> 00:23:20,350
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">the answer.</font>

458
00:23:22,400 --> 00:23:23,880
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">But back then, I was still naive.</font>

459
00:23:24,830 --> 00:23:26,000
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I knew very little</font>

460
00:23:26,110 --> 00:23:27,030
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">about love.</font>

461
00:23:28,200 --> 00:23:29,270
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I also didn't have the courage</font>

462
00:23:29,310 --> 00:23:30,550
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">to expose my feelings.</font>

463
00:23:31,270 --> 00:23:32,480
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">So I didn't even dare</font>

464
00:23:32,480 --> 00:23:33,350
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">to tell you his name.</font>

465
00:23:34,640 --> 00:23:35,480
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">But now,</font>

466
00:23:36,400 --> 00:23:37,440
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I have found the answer.</font>

467
00:23:38,920 --> 00:23:39,640
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Rest assured.</font>

468
00:23:40,880 --> 00:23:41,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">From now on,</font>

469
00:23:41,550 --> 00:23:42,960
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I will no longer be alone.</font>

470
00:23:53,000 --> 00:23:53,720
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Mr. Yan.</font>

471
00:23:54,400 --> 00:23:55,960
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You don't have to answer me right now.</font>

472
00:23:56,550 --> 00:23:58,550
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I only hope you can think it over</font>

473
00:23:58,960 --> 00:24:00,270
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">and be true to yourself.</font>

474
00:24:01,110 --> 00:24:02,590
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Whenever you have the answer</font>

475
00:24:02,790 --> 00:24:03,830
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">and figure it out,</font>

476
00:24:04,880 --> 00:24:05,790
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">you don't have to tell me.</font>

477
00:24:06,880 --> 00:24:08,070
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You know</font>

478
00:24:09,590 --> 00:24:10,440
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">who you should tell.</font>

479
00:24:11,720 --> 00:24:12,350
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Madam Hua.</font>

480
00:24:13,790 --> 00:24:14,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I have told my answer</font>

481
00:24:15,510 --> 00:24:16,750
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">to Hua Zhi.</font>

482
00:24:17,960 --> 00:24:19,160
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">At that time, you wanted me to be brave.</font>

483
00:24:20,350 --> 00:24:21,200
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">But I hesitated,</font>

484
00:24:21,640 --> 00:24:22,200
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">wavered,</font>

485
00:24:23,030 --> 00:24:24,110
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">and hurt her feelings.</font>

486
00:24:25,200 --> 00:24:26,720
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">We both wasted so much time.</font>

487
00:24:29,000 --> 00:24:29,880
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">From now on,</font>

488
00:24:31,070 --> 00:24:31,960
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I will cherish</font>

489
00:24:32,000 --> 00:24:33,350
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">every second and every moment</font>

490
00:24:34,550 --> 00:24:35,270
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">that I spend with her.</font>

491
00:24:48,590 --> 00:24:49,240
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I criticized</font>

492
00:24:49,480 --> 00:24:51,000
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">the Security Bureau,</font>

493
00:24:52,030 --> 00:24:54,200
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">which ruined my family.</font>

494
00:24:54,960 --> 00:24:55,680
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Now,</font>

495
00:24:56,550 --> 00:24:58,200
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">the Commander of the Security Bureau</font>

496
00:24:58,640 --> 00:25:00,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">is with my granddaughter.</font>

497
00:25:01,070 --> 00:25:02,550
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You never know what will happen next.</font>

498
00:25:03,200 --> 00:25:04,070
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I once said</font>

499
00:25:04,350 --> 00:25:06,240
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">the Security Bureau disregarded the law,</font>

500
00:25:06,480 --> 00:25:07,680
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">lynched people
and treated them like animals.</font>

501
00:25:08,550 --> 00:25:10,160
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">And it has become a scourge of Daqing.</font>

502
00:25:11,200 --> 00:25:12,400
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">What do you think of that?</font>

503
00:25:12,720 --> 00:25:13,480
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">In fact, that day,</font>

504
00:25:14,680 --> 00:25:15,790
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I heard everything you said
behind the curtain.</font>

505
00:25:17,590 --> 00:25:18,790
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Taking charge of the Security Bureau</font>

506
00:25:19,590 --> 00:25:20,750
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">was not what I wanted
in the first place.</font>

507
00:25:22,310 --> 00:25:23,750
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">But as the Commander,</font>

508
00:25:24,440 --> 00:25:25,440
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">not for a single day did I ever forget</font>

509
00:25:25,480 --> 00:25:26,160
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">what you said.</font>

510
00:25:27,110 --> 00:25:28,160
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">The Security Bureau now</font>

511
00:25:28,830 --> 00:25:29,680
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">is no longer the one</font>

512
00:25:29,750 --> 00:25:31,000
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">that you criticized.</font>

513
00:25:37,960 --> 00:25:38,920
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">If you don't believe it,</font>

514
00:25:39,070 --> 00:25:40,310
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">you can go see for yourself.</font>

515
00:25:43,680 --> 00:25:44,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I think that's not necessary.</font>

516
00:25:45,350 --> 00:25:46,720
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">The one that Zhi chooses</font>

517
00:25:47,640 --> 00:25:48,400
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">must be a good man.</font>

518
00:25:49,160 --> 00:25:50,720
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Everything you do</font>

519
00:25:50,830 --> 00:25:51,720
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">is under the watch</font>

520
00:25:51,790 --> 00:25:52,720
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">of the people.</font>

521
00:25:54,070 --> 00:25:56,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">These years I have also heard</font>

522
00:25:57,070 --> 00:25:58,000
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">the reputation of the Security Bureau.</font>

523
00:25:59,030 --> 00:25:59,720
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Today,</font>

524
00:26:00,480 --> 00:26:02,160
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">please allow me to address you
not as 'Your Highness',</font>

525
00:26:03,160 --> 00:26:05,070
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">but rather as 'son'.</font>

526
00:26:07,480 --> 00:26:08,110
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Son.</font>

527
00:26:09,160 --> 00:26:09,830
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">The only wish</font>

528
00:26:10,830 --> 00:26:11,960
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">of mine</font>

529
00:26:12,960 --> 00:26:14,590
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">is for you to treat Zhi well.</font>

530
00:26:15,510 --> 00:26:16,030
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I surely will.</font>

