00:34:58,800 --> 00:34:59,230
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Will do.</font>

710
00:34:59,800 --> 00:35:00,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">It's true.</font>

711
00:35:00,590 --> 00:35:01,840
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You are really capable</font>

712
00:35:02,150 --> 00:35:03,230
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">when it comes to managing business.</font>

713
00:35:04,480 --> 00:35:05,800
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Zhi is at leisure now.</font>

714
00:35:06,230 --> 00:35:06,670
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Now I have to</font>

715
00:35:07,030 --> 00:35:08,030
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">shoulder the responsibility.</font>

716
00:35:08,280 --> 00:35:08,710
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Madam Xia.</font>

717
00:35:09,760 --> 00:35:10,760
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">This is the ledger for this month.</font>

718
00:35:11,710 --> 00:35:12,670
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">As usual,</font>

719
00:35:12,710 --> 00:35:13,440
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">just report the numbers to me</font>

720
00:35:13,710 --> 00:35:14,710
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">once you settle the accounts.</font>

721
00:35:14,880 --> 00:35:15,280
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Yes.</font>

722
00:35:15,800 --> 00:35:16,550
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Come with me to the accounting room.</font>

723
00:35:17,880 --> 00:35:18,710
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Qin, you're here.</font>

724
00:35:20,030 --> 00:35:20,550
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Mother.</font>

725
00:35:21,960 --> 00:35:22,880
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Enjoy yourselves.</font>

726
00:35:27,320 --> 00:35:29,030
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Once we collect
the money for this month,</font>

727
00:35:29,440 --> 00:35:30,670
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I will help you purchase the teahouse</font>

728
00:35:30,710 --> 00:35:31,960
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">on Wasp Lane.</font>

729
00:35:32,590 --> 00:35:34,030
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">There's no need to tell me all this.</font>

730
00:35:34,150 --> 00:35:35,360
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">It makes my head ache just hearing it.</font>

731
00:35:36,110 --> 00:35:36,840
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22"></font>

732
00:35:38,880 --> 00:35:39,670
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Spend it as you wish.</font>

733
00:35:40,670 --> 00:35:42,000
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">This is your money after all.</font>

734
00:35:42,550 --> 00:35:43,480
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You have a share in it too.</font>

735
00:35:44,440 --> 00:35:45,030
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Alright then.</font>

736
00:35:45,360 --> 00:35:46,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I'll go to the accounting room</font>

737
00:35:46,590 --> 00:35:47,840
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">and do the counting properly.</font>

738
00:35:48,400 --> 00:35:48,880
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Go ahead.</font>

739
00:35:51,440 --> 00:35:52,190
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Bolin.</font>

740
00:35:52,510 --> 00:35:53,710
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">My clothes got torn.</font>

741
00:35:53,760 --> 00:35:54,550
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">It needs mending.</font>

742
00:35:54,670 --> 00:35:55,840
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Have you seen my mother?</font>

743
00:35:56,230 --> 00:35:56,920
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Which one?</font>

744
00:35:57,320 --> 00:35:58,150
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Any of them would do.</font>

745
00:35:58,510 --> 00:35:59,840
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Aunt Qi is teaching at the academy.</font>

746
00:36:00,360 --> 00:36:01,360
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Ms. Qin is with Aunt Xia.</font>

747
00:36:01,440 --> 00:36:02,070
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">She's busy.</font>

748
00:36:02,440 --> 00:36:03,440
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I have to go.</font>

749
00:36:04,000 --> 00:36:04,440
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Grandfather.</font>

750
00:36:04,670 --> 00:36:05,190
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Grandfather.</font>

751
00:36:08,920 --> 00:36:10,320
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Well, everyone is busy now.</font>

752
00:36:17,960 --> 00:36:18,710
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You did wrong here.</font>

753
00:36:18,840 --> 00:36:19,590
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">The calculation is wrong.</font>

754
00:36:20,150 --> 00:36:20,880
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Find the mistake yourself.</font>

755
00:36:25,710 --> 00:36:26,400
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">This is not correct.</font>

756
00:36:26,400 --> 00:36:27,590
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Nianqiu, I come to settle the accounts.</font>

757
00:36:28,840 --> 00:36:29,360
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Fudong?</font>

758
00:36:29,510 --> 00:36:29,960
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Fudong.</font>

759
00:36:31,190 --> 00:36:31,840
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Where is Mr. Bai?</font>

760
00:36:32,760 --> 00:36:33,920
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">He needs to look after the kids at home.</font>

761
00:36:34,030 --> 00:36:34,800
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Can't leave them alone anyway.</font>

762
00:36:35,920 --> 00:36:36,480
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Fudong.</font>

763
00:36:37,000 --> 00:36:37,320
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Yingchun.</font>

764
00:36:37,320 --> 00:36:38,070
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Why are you here today?</font>

765
00:36:38,670 --> 00:36:39,320
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">To settle the accounts.</font>

766
00:36:39,880 --> 00:36:40,320
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Oh, apologies.</font>

767
00:36:40,510 --> 00:36:41,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">We should call you Madam Bai.</font>

768
00:36:42,070 --> 00:36:43,550
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You are teasing me again.</font>

769
00:36:50,630 --> 00:36:51,400
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">The profits</font>

770
00:36:51,400 --> 00:36:52,590
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">are so substantial this month.</font>

771
00:36:53,030 --> 00:36:53,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Yes.</font>

772
00:36:53,510 --> 00:36:54,550
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">That was because Shen Huan</font>

773
00:36:54,590 --> 00:36:55,960
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">created several new drinks.</font>

774
00:36:56,150 --> 00:36:56,840
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">They were popular.</font>

775
00:36:57,960 --> 00:36:59,320
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">And he is quite energetic.</font>

776
00:36:59,630 --> 00:37:01,030
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">During the day he directs puppet shows</font>

777
00:37:04,630 --> 00:37:05,280
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22"></font>

778
00:37:05,280 --> 00:37:06,800
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Baoxia is the most blessed one</font>

779
00:37:06,800 --> 00:37:07,840
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">among us all.</font>

780
00:37:18,110 --> 00:37:19,710
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Ling has sent a letter to Jin'e.</font>

781
00:37:20,760 --> 00:37:21,760
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Jin'e said</font>

782
00:37:21,960 --> 00:37:23,670
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">that we could read it too.</font>

783
00:37:24,480 --> 00:37:25,400
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">It says</font>

784
00:37:25,880 --> 00:37:27,190
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Mr. Zheng will soon</font>

785
00:37:27,360 --> 00:37:28,880
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">be reassigned back to the Capital.</font>

786
00:37:29,920 --> 00:37:32,030
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Ling is reluctant
to leave the children at the academy</font>

787
00:37:32,280 --> 00:37:33,440
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">and even cried several times.</font>

788
00:37:34,230 --> 00:37:35,190
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">It's best if they come back.</font>

789
00:37:36,030 --> 00:37:37,670
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Nowhere can compare
with the Imperial Capital.</font>

790
00:37:38,110 --> 00:37:39,440
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">How so?</font>

791
00:37:41,030 --> 00:37:41,960
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Yuniang and Pingyang</font>

792
00:37:42,000 --> 00:37:43,550
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">have been traveling around with Yuan.</font>

793
00:37:43,920 --> 00:37:44,670
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">They are</font>

794
00:37:44,960 --> 00:37:46,280
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">at the Dongting Lake these days.</font>

795
00:37:47,070 --> 00:37:48,030
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I don't understand why they'd take</font>

796
00:37:49,190 --> 00:37:50,150
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">such a little kid outside.</font>

797
00:37:52,510 --> 00:37:54,030
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">that they want to raise a girl like Zhi.</font>

798
00:37:59,510 --> 00:38:01,190
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Which maid brewed this?</font>

799
00:38:02,590 --> 00:38:03,280
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Where is Ms. Qiu?</font>

800
00:38:04,510 --> 00:38:05,190
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Where has she run off to?</font>

801
00:38:05,550 --> 00:38:06,480
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Stop.</font>

802
00:38:12,280 --> 00:38:13,670
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Ridiculous.</font>

803
00:38:14,400 --> 00:38:15,150
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I'm not used to this taste.</font>

804
00:38:15,760 --> 00:38:16,400
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Ask her to brew it for me.</font>

805
00:38:17,280 --> 00:38:17,960
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Seriously?</font>

806
00:38:19,510 --> 00:38:20,400
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You don't like it?</font>

807
00:38:21,150 --> 00:38:22,150
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Brew it yourself.</font>

808
00:38:27,030 --> 00:38:28,150
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Grandfather!</font>

809
00:38:28,230 --> 00:38:28,920
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">- Bolin.
- Hua Bolin.</font>

810
00:38:31,280 --> 00:38:31,630
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Father!</font>

811
00:38:31,880 --> 00:38:32,550
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">- Mother!
- Why are you running?</font>

812
00:38:33,110 --> 00:38:34,360
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">[Hua Yizheng's Expostulation]
Grandfather's books have been printed.</font>

813
00:38:34,840 --> 00:38:36,070
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">And they're selling like crazy
in the Directorate of Education.</font>

814
00:38:36,400 --> 00:38:37,630
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I barely managed to buy one.</font>

815
00:38:38,000 --> 00:38:39,030
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I'll show it to Grandfather.</font>

816
00:38:40,110 --> 00:38:40,630
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Go!</font>

817
00:38:43,960 --> 00:38:44,670
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Those manuscripts</font>

818
00:38:47,280 --> 00:38:48,000
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22"></font>

819
00:38:48,440 --> 00:38:49,360
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">they have been printed into books.</font>

820
00:38:49,960 --> 00:38:50,960
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I want to send one to her,</font>

821
00:38:51,920 --> 00:38:53,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">but I don't know where she is.</font>

822
00:38:53,510 --> 00:38:54,030
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Yeah.</font>

823
00:38:54,110 --> 00:38:55,110
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">It's all thanks to Zhi.</font>

824
00:38:55,920 --> 00:38:56,480
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Yingzhen.</font>

825
00:38:57,760 --> 00:38:59,030
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Whatever you say goes.</font>

826
00:38:59,670 --> 00:39:00,630
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">It was my fault just now.</font>

827
00:39:01,280 --> 00:39:01,630
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Come.</font>

828
00:39:02,030 --> 00:39:02,480
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Let's sit down.</font>

829
00:39:12,000 --> 00:39:12,710
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Are you serious?</font>

830
00:39:12,920 --> 00:39:14,710
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You don't care about Boli's studies,</font>

831
00:39:15,320 --> 00:39:16,960
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">but care a lot about</font>

832
00:39:17,320 --> 00:39:18,480
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">these orphans' homework.</font>

833
00:39:19,150 --> 00:39:21,230
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I don't have to worry about Boli.</font>

834
00:39:22,000 --> 00:39:23,360
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Ergui is taking care of him.</font>

835
00:39:24,030 --> 00:39:25,030
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">If you ask me,</font>

836
00:39:25,510 --> 00:39:26,840
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I want him to go outside</font>

837
00:39:26,960 --> 00:39:28,440
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">and exercise every day</font>

838
00:39:28,550 --> 00:39:29,630
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">to build a strong body.</font>

839
00:39:30,440 --> 00:39:32,440
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">These carefree days of youth</font>

840
00:39:34,280 --> 00:39:34,800
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">As for these children</font>

841
00:39:34,840 --> 00:39:36,030
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">from the orphanage,</font>

842
00:39:36,920 --> 00:39:38,000
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">if we don't care for them,</font>

843
00:39:38,510 --> 00:39:40,400
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">then no one will.</font>

844
00:39:41,440 --> 00:39:42,590
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Please go</font>

845
00:39:42,710 --> 00:39:43,550
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">and return the homework</font>

846
00:39:43,760 --> 00:39:44,480
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">to those children.</font>

847
00:39:45,230 --> 00:39:46,110
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Ask those who got</font>

848
00:39:46,280 --> 00:39:47,360
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">the second grade to see me.</font>

849
00:39:49,480 --> 00:39:50,110
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Fine.</font>

850
00:39:50,760 --> 00:39:51,840
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Madam Qi.</font>

851
00:39:54,190 --> 00:39:55,190
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Come on.</font>

852
00:39:55,280 --> 00:39:55,960
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Go!</font>

853
00:39:56,190 --> 00:39:58,070
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Go for it!</font>

854
00:39:58,400 --> 00:39:59,920
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You can do this!</font>

855
00:40:00,480 --> 00:40:01,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Children.</font>

856
00:40:01,590 --> 00:40:02,760
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Stop for a moment.</font>

857
00:40:03,150 --> 00:40:03,550
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Come here.</font>

858
00:40:03,800 --> 00:40:04,880
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Claim your homework.</font>

859
00:40:06,000 --> 00:40:07,280
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Don't rush.</font>

860
00:40:07,960 --> 00:40:08,800
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Liao Hongxue.</font>

861
00:40:09,590 --> 00:40:10,280
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Here.</font>

862
00:40:11,670 --> 00:40:12,760
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Li Fengfeng.</font>

863
00:40:13,670 --> 00:40:14,230
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Here.</font>

864
00:40:14,710 --> 00:40:15,760
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Mingjing.</font>

865
00:40:16,400 --> 00:40:17,440
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Madam Qi said</font>

866
00:40:17,760 --> 00:40:18,400
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">those who got the second grade</font>

867
00:40:18,440 --> 00:40:19,630
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">need to go find her.</font>

868
00:40:20,230 --> 00:40:21,230
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Those who got the first grade</font>

869
00:40:21,280 --> 00:40:22,550
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">can get a pastry.</font>

870
00:40:23,510 --> 00:40:24,070
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">We can have pastries.</font>

871
00:40:24,070 --> 00:40:25,000
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Go for your pastries.</font>

872
00:40:25,230 --> 00:40:25,800
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I want one too.</font>

873
00:40:25,880 --> 00:40:26,440
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Me too.</font>

874
00:40:26,800 --> 00:40:27,800
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I'm going to get a pastry.</font>

875
00:40:28,360 --> 00:40:30,070
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Ms. Qiu, I got the second grade.</font>

876
00:40:31,070 --> 00:40:32,000
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Don't cry.</font>

877
00:40:32,360 --> 00:40:33,000
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Later,</font>

878
00:40:33,000 --> 00:40:34,590
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I will go with you to see Madam Qi,</font>

879
00:40:34,590 --> 00:40:35,190
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">okay?</font>

880
00:40:36,110 --> 00:40:37,000
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Those who got the second grade</font>

881
00:40:37,030 --> 00:40:38,230
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">can also get a pastry.</font>

882
00:40:38,360 --> 00:40:38,760
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Let's go.</font>

883
00:40:41,510 --> 00:40:42,670
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I can have a pastry too.</font>

884
00:40:43,510 --> 00:40:44,150
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I will take one.</font>

885
00:41:10,920 --> 00:41:11,630
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Greetings, Your Majesty.</font>

886
00:41:12,110 --> 00:41:12,920
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">No need for formality, Shaoyao.</font>

887
00:41:15,360 --> 00:41:15,840
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">County Princess.</font>

888
00:41:16,360 --> 00:41:17,030
